  {
    "id": 3,
    "offset": 367016,
    "slot_size": 272,
    "data_size": 268,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "Even[SP]the[SP]part[SP]about[SP]rumors[SP]coming[SP]true,\nand[SP]the[SP]stuff[SP]about[SP]the[SP]future...?[1205][001E][SP]That's\ntoo[SP]much[SP]for[SP]it[SP]to[SP]be[SP]a[SP]coincidence.",
